Class Actor

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.cae.jsdf.v1_6.Actor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SDFType

    @JsonClassDescription(value="A special kind of model which can have a scripted motion. This includes both global waypoint type animations and skeleton animations.")
public final class Actor
extends Object
implements SDFType
    A special kind of model which can have a scripted motion. This includes both global waypoint type animations and skeleton animations.
